high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the sink.
Pick up a spatula on the counter.
Put the spatula on a plate on the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Turn and go to the table.
Put the plate on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a plate with a spatula to the table.

high_descs: Walk through the kitchen, to the counter top before the sink, on your right.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Put the spatula on the blue plate on the counter.
Pick up the blue plate with the spatula on it.
Turn to your right and go to the end of the room, then turn to your right again and go to the white table across from you.
Place the plate with the spatula on it, on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing a spatula on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the spatula next to the sink.
Put the spatula hand-up on the square blue plate.
Pick up the square blue plate with the spatula on it.
Make a right, then another right at the fridge to end up at the white table.
Place the blue plate and spatula down on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a spatula handle-up on the blue square plate to move to the white table.
